txt.en: 'Haha! We kicked the hornet's nest now, haven't we, [placeholder]? The enemy is frantically swarming out of Gundabad in a paltry attempt to block our forward progress. Do what you can to thin their ranks. Anything you manage will be of great help to the Gabil'akkâ!'
'Good work! Surely their fear of our might is much increased. We may not rest yet, however, but must continue until Gundabad is ours!'
Defeat foes in the War of Three Peaks ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Hlóthi is in Annak-khurfu in southern Elderslade.\n\nReturn to Hlóthi.
Defeated foes in the War of Three Peaks ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Anything you can do to thin the enemy's numbers will greatly help us.'
Foes in the War of Three Peaks must be defeated to help the Gabil'akkâ press forward to Gundabad.
March on Gundabad: Securing the Slade
Foes can be found throughout the War of Three Peaks.\n\nHlóthi has asked you to defeat foes in the War of Three Peaks.
